Bayan haka, guguwar Rosa za ta ci gaba da shiga Mexico a matsayin guguwar ruwan sama, kafin ta kai iyakar Arizona a farkon safiyar Talata a matsayin ruwan sama mai zafi, wanda zai ci gaba da wucewa ta Arizona zuwa kudancin Utah a ranar Talata da dare.
"Babban haɗarin da ake tsammani daga hadari na Rose, ko kuma daga abin da ya rage, shi ne ruwan sama mai yawa a Jihar California, kudu maso yammacin Sonora da kuma kudancin yammacin hamada a Amurka", in ji Cibiyar Hurricane ta Kasa.
