Turai ta ci gaba da kaiwa 10-6 zuwa ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup
Turai na da fa'ida mai kyau a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder bayan ta kammala wasan hudu da na hudu a ranar Asabar da ta yi 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Tommy Plitwood da kuma Wrenchsky Molinary sun jagoranci canji tare da nasara biyu akan Tiger Woods mai gwagwarmaya, kuma sun haɓaka rata a Le Golf National zuwa maki hudu.
