Flightwood shine farkon ɗan wasan Turai da ya ci maki huɗu a jere, yayin da shi da Millinery, waɗanda suka sami lakabi na Hollywood bayan wata karshen mako mai ban mamaki, su ne kawai biyu da suka ci maki huɗu daga cikin wasannin buɗe huɗu a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasannin hudu, sun ci gaba da aiki tare cikin kyakkyawar jituwa don doke Woods da kuma dan wasan Amurka, Raison DeCambaau da karin sakamako mai ban mamaki na 5 da 4.
Woods, wanda ya yi wasan biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna kyakkyawan sakamako, amma ya ci nasara a wasanni 19 na hudu da hudu, da kuma wasanni bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya yi barci a lokacin wasan hudu na yau da safe, ya dawo don ya shiga Henrik Stenson a wasan hudu don ya doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Kofke, na biyu da na uku a duniya.
Amma, ba duk abin da ya yi sauƙi ba ga 'yan wasan Turai a cikin yanayi mai kyau da kuma iska mai sauƙi da ke kudu maso yammacin Paris.
